sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Jupyter Workbench)
    participant SDK as CodeFlare SDK<br/>(Python Library)
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant AWCtrl as CodeFlare Operator<br/>(AppWrapper Controller)
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Node<br/>8265/TCP Dashboard<br/>10001/TCP Client

    Note over User,RayHead: Flow 1: Cluster Creation (with AppWrapper)

    User->>SDK: Cluster(ClusterConfiguration(...))
    SDK->>K8s: Check RayCluster CRD exists<br/>Bearer Token
    K8s-->>SDK: CRD confirmed
    SDK->>K8s: List LocalQueues (kueue.x-k8s.io/v1beta1)<br/>Bearer Token
    K8s-->>SDK: Default LocalQueue resolved
    SDK->>SDK: Generate YAML from base-template.yaml<br/>+ ClusterConfiguration + Kueue labels
    SDK->>K8s: Create AppWrapper CR<br/>(workload.codeflare.dev/v1beta2)<br/>Bearer Token
    K8s-->>SDK: AppWrapper created
    AWCtrl->>KubeRay: Reconcile embedded RayCluster
    KubeRay->>K8s: Create head/worker Pods,<br/>Services, Routes

    Note over User,RayHead: Flow 2: Job Submission

    User->>SDK: cluster.job_submit(entrypoint)
    SDK->>K8s: List Routes/Ingresses<br/>Bearer Token
    K8s-->>SDK: Ray Dashboard URL discovered
    SDK->>RayHead: POST /api/jobs/ (submit job)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS via Route<br/>Bearer Token (OpenShift)
    RayHead-->>SDK: Job ID
    SDK->>RayHead: GET /api/jobs/{id}/status<br/>Bearer Token
    RayHead-->>SDK: Job status + logs
    SDK-->>User: Job results

    Note over User,RayHead: Flow 3: TLS Certificate Generation

    User->>SDK: cluster.connect_with_tls()
    SDK->>K8s: Read CA secret ({cluster}-ca-secret-*)<br/>Bearer Token
    K8s-->>SDK: CA cert + key
    SDK->>SDK: Generate client cert/key<br/>(cryptography library)
    SDK->>SDK: Write tls-{cluster}-{ns}/ locally<br/>Set RAY_USE_TLS env vars
    SDK->>RayHead: Connect via gRPC<br/>10001/TCP mTLS<br/>Client TLS cert
    RayHead-->>SDK: Interactive Ray session
